I am excited to apply for the Junior Full Stack React/Node.js Developer position at Dev Technology. With a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science and over two years of professional experience as a Senior Software Engineer, I have honed my skills in full stack application development, particularly with React and Node.js. My career objective aligns perfectly with your mission of driving client success through innovative technology solutions, and I am eager to contribute to your projects that support federal government initiatives.

During my tenure at Capgemini, I successfully migrated legacy applications to modern technologies using AWS and implemented responsive user interfaces with React.js and Angular, which improved user experience and productivity significantly. My experience with Agile methodologies has equipped me with the ability to collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams, ensuring that client needs are met while continuously learning and adapting to new technologies. Additionally, my hands-on projects, such as developing a full-stack application that reduced processing time by 30%, demonstrate my commitment to delivering quality solutions.

I am particularly drawn to Dev Technology's employee-centric culture and focus on community engagement, which resonates with my values of collaboration and social responsibility. I am confident that my technical skills, combined with my passion for solving complex software challenges, make me a strong fit for your team. I look forward to the opportunity to discuss how I can contribute to your mission and support your clients effectively.

I look forward to discussing how my technical skills and proactive mindset can align with SOCOTEC’s goals and contribute to your continued success.
